edu.nd.darts.cimon.database
Class MetricInfoTable

java.lang.Object
  edu.nd.darts.cimon.database.MetricInfoTable

public final class MetricInfoTable
extends Object

Defines the layout of the MetricInfo table of the database. This table stores general information about a metric or group of metrics, such as name, description, power usage, etc.

Author:
chris miller
See Also:
MetricsTable, MetricStatusTable
